<!-- Update the value of <% version = 4 %> in this comment when updating the what's new popup to make it appear again on launch -->
<input type="hidden" id="whatsNewVersion" value="<%=version%>"/>
<div id="whatsNewPopup"><div> <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-xmark" onclick="hideWhatsNew(<%=version%>)" style="position: absolute; right: 10px; top: 10px; cursor: pointer"></i>
    <h2>What's New</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><p>Interface Redesign! 🖌️</p>
            <ul>
                <li>New user interface! 📱</li>
                <li>Pin your bus to show it on the screen 📌</li>
                <li>The current wave is displayed on the bottom of the screen 🌊</li>
                <li>Open the dropdown menu at the top right ↗️</li>
                <li>When a wave is locked, the timer is now a progress bar ⌛</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><p>Arrival Time Predictions 🕰️</p>
            <ul>
                <li>If your bus has not yet arrived, a predicted arrival time is shown in gray text ⏱️</li>
                <li>The time is replaced with actual time once your bus has arrived 🎳</li>
                <li>This time is an average of the last 5 days, it may be off if your bus time varies often ❗</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><p>Bus Map & Bus Position 🧭</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Bus Map shows where your bus is parked in the bus lot 🗺️</li>
                <li>Position is displayed next to your bus status ⚓</li>
                <li>1 is at the front, larger numbers are further back ↔️</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><p>PiP Bus Data Overlay 📟</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Can be used over any app 📲</li>
                <li>Use skip and previous buttons to cycle through pinned buses on Android ⏮️⏭️</li>
                <li>On iPhones, use the stop button to cycle through pinned buses ⏹️</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><p>Other Changes ⁉️</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Announcement changes now send a notification 📣</li>
                <li>Chrome extension! Get it <a href="https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/bus-app/cgceeklcikhpejkbldnppbbnnjibokok">here</a> 🪀</li>
                <li>Dynamic background depending on weather 🌦️</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><p>Bug Fixes 🐞</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Fixed &quot;Your bus just left!&quot; notifications not sending 🔕</li>
                <li>Improved reliability of notifications, clicking the notification now opens the bus app 📳</li>
                <li>Fixed many loading indicators 🎺</li>
                <li>Notice a bug? Fill out the feedback form! it helps us a lot ✅</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>Have feedback or ideas? Send us an email at <a href="mailto:busappdevs@proton.me">busappdevs@proton.me</a> or fill out <a target="_blank" href="https://forms.gle/ffekcnoKTtAUMBic6">this feedback form</a></li>
    </ul>
    <br />
    <p>- 🚍 The Bus App Team</p>
    <br /><a class="generic-button" onclick="hideWhatsNew(<%=version%>)">Got It!</a>
</div></div>